rows.label: tlk43320341_02_msg0001
rows.name:
A few members of Iira showed up
in this town a little while ago.

rows.label: tlk43320341_02_msg0002
rows.name:
I was thinking of trying to arrest
them myself. But it was just me,
so I didn't have a hope.

rows.label: tlk43320341_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Looks like they're mobile enough to
appear anywhere they like though.

rows.label: tlk43320341_02_msg0004
rows.name:
They've got a really smart ship,
that's for sure. It's not made
out of a Divine Beast, either.

rows.label: tlk43320341_02_msg0005
rows.name:
It looked like a thing from another
era, if you ask me...Something using
some kind of forgotten technology.
